name: Hellen Robin
description: My name is hellen robin am 30 years old am single Originally from san jose but i live in Washington with my granny im a under trained nurse i consider myself to be a warm, open, thoughtful, genuine, and honest person. I thoroughly enjoy being silly and quirky as much as possible, but, on the other hand, enjoy heartfelt, genuine, thought-provoking conversations too. I have many opinions on so many various topics, and love engaging in banter on the many things that I find interesting.
